ent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104cui1665702732182.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cui1665702732182.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cui1665702732182.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"cui1665702732182\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      disable lws close\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Keep the master connection open after ending a lightweight session\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"cui1665702732182__topic_d55511e1_d55512e1_d55513e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cui1665702732182__p_d55514e1_d55515e1_d55516e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$ORA_PARAMS</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">= disable lws close</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cui1665702732182__p_d55517e1_d55518e1_d55519e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$ORA_PARAMS</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">= dlc</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cui1665702732182__section_fs5_tl4_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d403444e72\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cui1665702732182__p_d55523e1_d55524e1_d55525e1\">This option is only effective when using lightweight\n            sessions.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cui1665702732182__section_wgh_5l4_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d403444e81\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cui1665702732182__p_d55529e1_d55530e1_d55531e1\">By default the master connection is closed when the\n            last lightweight session is ended. To keep the master connection open this option needs\n            to be set.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic he